# Build-context filter for `podman build` / `docker build` invoked
# against the repository root with the official Containerfile at
# deploy/container/Containerfile.
#
# Goal: keep the upload to the builder small + reproducible.
# Anything genuinely needed for `cargo build --release --bin bvault`
# must NOT be excluded here.

# --- Heavy build outputs ---
target/
**/target/
debug/
**/debug/

# --- VCS metadata ---
.git/
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.gitmodules

# --- GUI / desktop bundle (server image does not include the GUI) ---
gui/node_modules/
gui/dist/
gui/src-tauri/target/

# --- External submodules not needed for the server build ---
# `plugins-ext/` is excluded from the Cargo workspace (see Cargo.toml),
# so the server build doesn't need it. `IronRDP` likewise.
plugins-ext/
IronRDP/

# --- Editor / OS noise ---
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
**/*.bak
**/*~

# --- Tests fixtures + docs are kept (some build scripts read them) ---
# Don't add `docs/` or `tests/` here without verifying nothing in the
# build path reads them.
